dy真.革命心態<br />\n<br />\n如果真係未Ready，咪一步步咁適應囉<br />\n當年辛亥革命，攻入D政府機關並宣佈真.新政府，都係一步步黎，先係湖北既省總部，再係其他省既總部，咁點解我地唔可以一區區咁黎，好似當年咁<span style=\"color: green;\">進入</span>各座政府建築啊？<br />\n<br />\n講到尾，我係想前線<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係對返住政權、目標</span></span>，犧牲都好，都要有意義，唔好畀仇恨搞到自己失焦同做無法達到目標既事。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">行動有意義、可以達成目標，和、勇先會多D人走返出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">(以上內容只是電影《辛亥革命》劇情討論與幻想劇情內容，請不要在現實參與違法活動)</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:41:22.000Z","msg":"幫手推吖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cebd1f8848c9d344cb7dc92e54db6871fb372d2","tid":1691374,"uid":14214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:44:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"630afff74073da387c44612cee336d99d03ea551","tid":1691374,"uid":231922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:54:08.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e9239b7bf822d838cba5f85ebec5f7c6b4d278b1","tid":1691374,"uid":231922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:54:34.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"08e46fdb0dea27a3dbe21351321990c2f439806b","tid":1691374,"uid":263018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"好劇情"},{"pid":"5d8c8e6ebc4435f43f33d5fb090a6fd73ebd1d8e","tid":1691374,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:02:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8713d5b32dbfbc1cfea696e51b598dcda9147520","tid":1691374,"uid":231922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗"},{"pid":"9d92fe3779433c5b86912375cf9f1dcd10653170","tid":1691374,"uid":58453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:42:34.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"99d60ca8f5b58d2477a5fe648ee9a453ada2d13d